headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Benefactor Serrano, BeeJay XL, Emperor Habanero, Fathom FQ 2
content: You’ve been casually stealing them ever since you first set foot on the streets of Los Santos and discovered you couldn’t be bothered to walk to the store. Now you’re a crime lord with more underground garage space than you know what to do with, it’s time you paid your respects: and what better way to show you remember where you came from than calling every one of these underrated classics your own?
